column5: This post is 100 percent me. I, like a lot of other comments here have really adapted to this new slower pace and work from Home life. I’ve been eating better, working out and my anxiety has improved a lot. I do want to golf and see friends and family but at the same time I’m very content with my life right now. It’s a weird situation to be in. Obviously, like you guys I don’t want convid to continue or anything like that, but there has definitely been some good that has come out of all of this.
